{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reason we left Auschwitz is a very awkward time, was like 2, 3 o'clock in the morning, is because the Russian front was-- we were already hearing some artillery firing, distant artillery firing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was some rejoicing, at least by the elders, that there was hopefully some kind of a relief coming, possibly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in any event, we were herded out of the barracks at-- late-- late at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I suppose it was past midnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know it was dark, very dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Think it was around September, late September in '44.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were-- we were marched for a long time to-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] to some alley.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not get our numbers, because we were evacuated at a very fast pace.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were part of a-- of a transport that never got numbers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were never stamped with-- tattooed with numbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were going through this particular area and section, and-- where we saw women standing on the right side when we were marching, walking, hollering out to us names.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schleimer, Ben, is that you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is that you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were hoping to hear maybe the answer of a loved one, or friend, or child that was being transported out, and that to-- they wanted to confirm or identify that they were still alive.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So all we heard was these names being thrown at us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we, in turn, was hollering out, Schprensa, Hankel, Mama, whatever we could say to be able to hopefully say, oh, then, we didn't hear that, we said, [NON-ENGLISH] did you know if this one survived.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, while we were walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is while we're walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
